==English==

===Noun===
'''misrepresentation'''
# [[erroneous|Erroneous]] or [[false]] [[representation]]; an [[unfair]] or [[dishonest]] [[account]] or [[exposition]]; a false [[statement]]: as, to injure one's character by misrepresentations.
# Incorrect or [[unfaithful]] representation in the capacity of [[agent]] or official [[representative]], as of a principal in a matter of business, or of constituents in legislation.
# In map-making, [[faultiness]] in a [[map-projection]], estimated with regard to its [[unequal]] [[scale]] in different parts and to its [[distortion]] of [[angle]]s.

====Related terms====
* [[misrepresent]]
* [[misrepresentative]]
* [[misrepresenter]]

